code: @Override public TypeSerializerSchemaCompatibility<Map<K, V>> resolveSchemaCompatibility(TypeSerializer<Map<K, V>> newSerializer) {     if (newSerializer instanceof MapSerializer) {         List<Tuple2<TypeSerializer<?>, TypeSerializerSnapshot<?>>> nestedSerializersAndConfigs = getNestedSerializersAndConfigs().         // redirect the compatibility check to the new MapSerializerSnapshot         return CompositeTypeSerializerUtil.delegateCompatibilityCheckToNewSnapshot(newSerializer, new MapSerializerSnapshot<>(), nestedSerializersAndConfigs.get(0).f1, nestedSerializersAndConfigs.get(1).f1).     } else {         return super.resolveSchemaCompatibility(newSerializer).     } }
